## AGENT ACTIVATION

Invoke specific agents by including their directive in your prompt:

- `@architect` - System design, repository structure, API design
- `@builder` - Implementation, coding, feature development
- `@qa` - Testing, code review, bug detection
- `@ux` - Design review, accessibility, visual polish
- `@docs` - Documentation, user guides, API specs
- `@devops` - Deployment, CI/CD, monitoring
- `@support` - Issue triage, user support, maintenance

### Multi-Agent Workflows
For complex tasks, agents can be chained:
- "Build new feature" → @architect → @builder → @qa → @docs
- "Fix production issue" → @support → @builder → @qa → @devops
- "UI overhaul" → @ux → @builder → @qa

